jobInfo.postDescription:
Injection molding engineer
Job responsibilities：
1Be responsible for drawing and checking new product design stage to reduce the cost of new product development；
2Be responsible for solving process problems in new product development stage and propose modification strategy for mold problem；
3Responsible for the improvement and optimization of the molding process and equipment；
4Provide technical support to molding department；
5Responsible for the import of new equipment, and correspond to new equipment failure during warranty period；
6Be responsible for standardization of molding technical documents and prepare standard documents such as process documents and equipment inspection。
Job requirements：
1Bachelor degree or above, major in polymer material, material molding, mold design, mechanical design, etc；
2More than 3 years working experience in injection molding process is preferred；
3Understand the structure and performance of injection mold and injection molding machine, machine debugging, proficiency in new product testing and improvement of process performance；
4Proficient in injection molding process improvement, understanding of plastic material properties, rich experience in quality control and inspection；
5Strong sense of responsibility, steadfast and willing to bear hardships and stand hard work, strong sense of teamwork and communication and coordination；
6Familiar with AUTOCAD, PRO/E and other graphics software。
jobInfo.address: 上海奉贤区上海金鑫生物科技有限公司211号

brandComInfo.introduce: 上海金鑫生物科技有限公司是生物科技、医用耗材、实验室、生命科学、分子生物学、临床检验和研究实验用一次性耗材的专业生产厂家。公司拥有高素质、国际化的研发团队、生产管理人员和高精度的数字控制生产设备。产品覆盖自动化吸头、普通吸头、PCR板（96、384等）、PCR管、培养板（皿）、样品管、离心管、实验室试剂、医用耗材及医疗器械。产品质量已经达到或超过国际同类产品水平。公司拥有十万级无尘车间2000平方米，实验室300平方米，生产设备和模具齐全，年产值达到13000万元以上。公司先后通过ISO9001质量管理体系认证、ISO14001环境管理体系认证，ISO13485医疗器械管理认证、欧盟CE认证。公司目前产品供不应求，市场广阔，发掘潜力巨大，随着一带一路的发展，国际市场也迎来良好的开发机遇，整体的市场发展前景非常好。公司正处在一个快速发展期，并在不远的将来力主打造一个产品领先，效益优良，管理高效，并有一支优秀团队的上市企业，欢迎广大有识之士、有志之士加入
